<topic id="topic35">
   <title>Email Alerts</title>
   <body>
      <p>The following parameters configure the system to send email alerts for fatal error
            events, such as a segment going down or a server crash and reset.</p>
      <simpletable id="kh171646">
         <strow>
            <stentry>
               <p>
                  <codeph>gp_email_from</codeph>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <codeph>gp_email_smtp_password</codeph>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <codeph>gp_email_smtp_server</codeph>
               </p>
            </stentry>
            <stentry>
               <p>
                  <codeph>gp_email_smtp_userid</codeph>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <codeph>gp_email_to</codeph>
               </p>
            </stentry>
         </strow>
      </simpletable>
   </body>
</topic>